'''水芫花属'''{{notetag|1={{標音|字=芫|注音=ㄩㄢˊ |拼音=yuán |同音字=元}}}}（學名：{{lang|la|''Pemphis''}}）是[[千屈菜科|千屈菜科]]下的一属，主要生长在沿海地区，1775年提出<ref name=ipni2>''Char. Gen. Pl.'' 34. 1775 {{cite web |url=http://www.ipni.org:80/ipni/idPlantNameSearch.do?id=554064-1 |title=Plant Name Details for ''Pemphis acidula'' |work=IPNI |accessdate=November 21, 2009 |archive-date=2017-11-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171109191312/http://www.ipni.org/ipni/idPlantNameSearch.do?id=554064-1 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。水芫花属有极高的适应性，根据环境因素不同，它可以延伸枝条，生长为[[灌木|灌木]]或矮[[树|树]]<ref name=fao>{{cite book |title=Mangrove Guidebook for Southeast Asia |author=Wim Giesen |coauthors=Stephan Wulffraat, Max Zieren, Liesbeth Scholten |chapter=Part 2: Description - Trees & shrubs |publisher=FAO, Regional Office for Asia and the Pacific; Wetlands International |year=2006 |ISBN=974-7946-85-8 |location=Bangkok |url=http://www.fao.org/docrep/010/ag132e/ag132e00.htm |accessdate=November 21, 2009 |archive-date=2011-07-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110729205819/http://www.fao.org/docrep/010/ag132e/ag132e00.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

